[10/02/2018 20:57:11] <font color="#ffffff">-Sí, claro.</font>
[10/02/2018 20:57:37] <font color="#ffffff">-(Señora Caterina!</font>
[10/02/2018 20:57:40] <font color="#ffffff">(Señora Caterina!</font>
[10/02/2018 20:57:42] <font color="#ffffff">-¿Quién es?</font>
[10/02/2018 20:57:44] <font color="#ffffff">-(Salga!</font>
